
Inspired by "A very popular BBQ sauce"


Double Batch

3 cups sugar
4 tbsp Molassas
3 cups ketchup 
1 cup red wine vinegar
1 cup water
2 tablespoon Worcestershire sauce
8 Teaspoons (Modified) Dry Mustard
4 teaspoons paprika
4 teaspoons salt
3 teaspoons black pepper
1 tsp  Dave's Temporary Insanity Sauce

Boil 5 min

Yields approx 4 2C mason jars.  Put them in the freezer, they wont freeze.
